      "role": "user",
      "content": "i tried some water but i still feel kinda clumsy with my hands and the words just wont come out right. i dont really want to go to a hospital and wait for hours in this heat if i dont have to. is there like a specific amount of electrolytes or something i should take to fix this quickly so i can just nap it off?",
